  "body": "relates to #11431 \"Migrate account to a regular keycard from logged out \"Manage keys and storage\"\n\nWhen solving #11431 we intentionally left out the case where the user wants to keep its data base when migrating. So the user is forced to reset its database and the check box is checked and greyed out in flow like this https://www.figma.com/file/dEIljL7UPbXgsZUA0Q4qlE5E/Onboarding?node-id=8218%3A7450\n\nThis issue is about enabling the user to keep its database\n- having \"reset database\" unchecked by default \n- letting the user checks it or not \n\nFigma design \nhttps://www.figma.com/file/dEIljL7UPbXgsZUA0Q4qlE5E/Onboarding?node-id=8218%3A8089",
